---
source: crates/runtime/tests/models/s3_vectors.rs
expression: replace_s3_vector_index_names(&formatted)
---
+---------------+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| plan_type     | plan                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            |
+---------------+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| logical_plan  | Projection: vector_search(delivery, Utf8("wrong location")).message.body, vector_search(delivery, Utf8("wrong location")).attempt_count, vector_search(delivery, Utf8("wrong location")).message.status, vector_search(delivery, Utf8("wrong location")).package_weight_kg, round(vector_search(delivery, Utf8("wrong location"))._score,Int64(1))                                                              |
|               |   Sort: vector_search(delivery, Utf8("wrong location")).package_weight_kg DESC NULLS FIRST, vector_search(delivery, Utf8("wrong location"))._score DESC NULLS FIRST, fetch=10                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |
|               |     Projection: vector_search(delivery, Utf8("wrong location")).message.body, vector_search(delivery, Utf8("wrong location")).attempt_count, vector_search(delivery, Utf8("wrong location")).message.status, vector_search(delivery, Utf8("wrong location")).package_weight_kg, round(vector_search(delivery, Utf8("wrong location"))._score, Int64(1)), vector_search(delivery, Utf8("wrong location"))._score |
|               |       TableScan: vector_search(delivery, Utf8("wrong location")) projection=[_score, attempt_count, message.body, message.status, package_weight_kg], full_filters=[vector_search(delivery, Utf8("wrong location")).attempt_count > Int64(1), vector_search(delivery, Utf8("wrong location")).package_weight_kg > Float64(5), vector_search(delivery, Utf8("wrong location")).message.status = Utf8("FAILED")]  |
| physical_plan | ProjectionExec: expr=[message.body@0 as message.body, attempt_count@1 as attempt_count, message.status@2 as message.status, package_weight_kg@3 as package_weight_kg, round(vector_search(delivery, Utf8("wrong location"))._score,Int64(1))@4 as round(vector_search(delivery, Utf8("wrong location"))._score,Int64(1))]                                                                                       |
|               |   SortPreservingMergeExec: [package_weight_kg@3 DESC, _score@5 DESC], fetch=10                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |
|               |     SortExec: TopK(fetch=10), expr=[package_weight_kg@3 DESC, _score@5 DESC], preserve_partitioning=[true]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |
|               |       ProjectionExec: expr=[message.body@2 as message.body, attempt_count@1 as attempt_count, message.status@3 as message.status, package_weight_kg@4 as package_weight_kg, round(_score@0, 1) as round(vector_search(delivery, Utf8("wrong location"))._score,Int64(1)), _score@0 as _score]                                                                                                                   |
|               |         RepartitionExec: partitioning=RoundRobinBatch(3), input_partitions=1                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |
|               |           ProjectionExec: expr=[_score@3 as _score, attempt_count@2 as attempt_count, message.body@4 as message.body, message.status@0 as message.status, package_weight_kg@1 as package_weight_kg]                                                                                                                                                                                                             |
|               |             HashJoinExec: mode=CollectLeft, join_type=Left, accumulator=MinMaxLeftAccumulator, on=[(event.id@0, event.id@0)], filter=attempt_count@2 > 1 AND package_weight_kg@1 > 5 AND message.status@0 = FAILED, projection=[message.status@1, package_weight_kg@2, attempt_count@3, _score@4, message.body@6]                                                                                               |
|               |               CoalescePartitionsExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            |
|               |                 ProjectionExec: expr=[key@3 as event.id, message.status@0 as message.status, package_weight_kg@1 as package_weight_kg, attempt_count@2 as attempt_count, 1 - distance@4 as _score]                                                                                                                                                                                                              |
|               |                   CooperativeExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |
|               |                     RepartitionExec: partitioning=RoundRobinBatch(3), input_partitions=1                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |
|               |                       BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |
|               |                         CooperativeExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |
|               |                           S3VectorsQueryExec (INDEX_NAME_1): filter={$and:[{attempt_count:{$gt:1}},{package_weight_kg:{$gt:5.0}},{message.status:{$eq:"FAILED"}}]} limit=100                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |
|               |               SchemaCastScanExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |
|               |                 BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |
|               |                   DataSourceExec: partitions=1, partition_sizes=[1]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |
|               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |
+---------------+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
